T16TD4443E:360b-0: @360b ` / mig 'byed mthong ba don ldan bzhugs so /
T16TD4443E:360b-4: // / * // rgya gar sh'a dzang gi sman pa yul ba ri bu ra nas 'ongs pa'i ma na ho'i lag len zin bris su dgod pa ni /
T16TD4443E:360b-5: de la sman dpyad zas spyod bzhi la /
T16TD4443E:360b-10: dang por dgongs mo nyal nas sang mig mi 'byed kyi bar du zas skom gyi rigs bkag / sprin med nyi mo dro sar nad pa dang sman pa gnyis stan bde bar bsdad /
T16TD4443E:360b-13: me hrag du ba med pa /
T16TD4443E:360b-20: nang gi mig sman la bya phur leb 'dra ba /
T16TD4443E:360b-21: shing sman ganda pa ta gsum /
T16TD4443E:360b-22: rnga mong gi ko lpags kyi rngar /
T16TD4443E:361a-0: @361a * // rdza rngar 'jam pa rnams bsags rjes /
T16TD4443E:361a-1: nad pa dang sman pa gnyis kyi lham phud /
T16TD4443E:361a-2: sman pa'i lag pa gtsang bar bkrus /
T16TD4443E:361a-3: nas phud gnyis ka'i lag tu thogs nas gsol 'debs bden bdar brjod nas nas 'thor /
T16TD4443E:361a-4: yung ba brdar nas chu dang sbyar bas mig gang 'byed kyi smin ma'i ltag la byugs /
T16TD4443E:361a-5: de rjes mig g-yon ma lta bu 'byed na sman pa'i bus mo g-yas pa bslang zhing /
T16TD4443E:361a-6: nad pa'i lag pa spar 'dzings kyis bzung /
T16TD4443E:361a-7: de'i rjes mig gi 'grib kyi thad g-yon phyed na g-yon zur /
T16TD4443E:361a-8: dkar nag nas gang gi mtshams su gtsags bur dar dkar gyi skud pas sked bcings byas pa'i steng du rgya gram brgyab pa'i rtse nas nas phyed tsam mthong ba des bsnun nas pags pa phigs pa byas rjes thur ma bra bo 'dra bas tshad dar skud kyi mtshams su sleb pa rgyal mor btang /
T16TD4443E:361a-9: de nas rten 'brel gyi sog ma dkar po gcig gi sked pa gtubs nas nad pa dang rang nyid kyi bar la sog ma lag g-yas kyi de g-yon dang g-yon gyi de g-yas la bskyur rjes /
T16TD4443E:361a-10: lag g-yon gyis mig lpags yar 'then pa dang /
T16TD4443E:361a-11: g-yas kyis thur ma rgyal mo'i sgrib byed 'phan ltar bsgril bas thur mar sgrib byed 'khril nas rgyal mo nag sing nge byung ba dang thur ma'i sgab nas bteg bteg byed pa dang lag g-yon gyis mig gang 'byed kyi tshog sgang du sdeg sdeg byas pas 'grib log byung na sngar ltar bsgril nas bzhag / de nas mig gi mthong byed du rdzas kha dog sna tshogs pa che ba chung ba'i bar rim par bstan pas phra rags so sor dbye 'byed thub pa yod /
T16TD4443E:361a-12: de rjes mig la srin bal chur sbyangs ba bkab /
T16TD4443E:361a-13: me mdangs kyi bsros pas 'grib byed thon sla ba 'ong /
T16TD4443E:361a-14: de nas thur ma tshur bsgril nas bton /
T16TD4443E:361a-15: thur rtse yung ba'i chur bcug bas sgrib byed thur mar 'khril nas dngos su mthong ba yong /
T16TD4443E:361a-17: (rgya gar skad la rnyo don dzo ti) shin sman ginda pa ta (ni m'a'i) rnams chu thigs gnyis gsum rdo 'jam po'i steng blug par rim bzhin brdar ba'i skyo ma sngar gyi thur ma brgyab par bslan /
T16TD4443E:361b-0: de'i rjes srin bal @361b chur sbyangs bkab de steng ras dkar yung ba'i khu bar bcug pa bkab /
T16TD4443E:361b-1: rgyal mo dmar nag byung na dar dkar tshva snum bsres par spags pa bkab /
T16TD4443E:361b-2: dkar po byung na mtshal dkar ma btul ba dang dung gnyis brdar ba'i skyo ma gong ltar bslan /
T16TD4443E:361b-3: de nas srin bal chur sbyangs yung ba'i chur ras spags pa rim par bkab steng ras dkar gyis mig 'bras bkab /
T16TD4443E:361b-8: dngul gsum po mi gcig gis mgo thog tu bzhag nas /
T16TD4443E:361b-18: zhes pa tshar gsum bzlas la mig gi steng du phu gsum rgyab pas mig gi nad zug dang bgegs sogs zhi bar byed pa yin /
T16TD4443E:361b-19: gri chung nad pa'i rkang 'og tu 'dren /
T16TD4443E:361b-20: yang mig rus dang mig na na /
T16TD4443E:361b-21: tsan dan dmar po dang yung ba /
T16TD4443E:361b-22: rgya gar gyi btsag yug brdar ba'i skyo man sar byugs /
T16TD4443E:361b-23: zas skom chu grang gi zan bya sgong tsam dang /
T16TD4443E:361b-24: rtsam pa sman tsha btab pa'i tsha ba bardi ba nyin re kha skom na thug pa phor pa gsum re tsam gang dgos gtong /
T16TD4443E:361b-25: zhag gsum gyi bar zas skyom 'di ma gtogs mi byed /
T16TD4443E:361b-26: spyod lam nyin mo gnyid mi nyal /
T16TD4443E:361b-27: ldan pa g-yas g-yon phab nas mi sdod /
T16TD4443E:361b-28: dgongs mo nyal sa steng shod la 'gro dgos yod tshe dal bus phyin nas nyal zhing rkang pa brkyangs chog / de nyin nas bzung zhag gsum gyi bar mig sman mig 'byed pa'i dus dang dgongs ja khar mig kha phye nas rdzas phra rags bstan pas gsal bar yong /
T16TD4443E:361b-29: de'i rjes mig sman re brgyab nas dkris ma sngar bzhin byed /
T16TD4443E:361b-30: rlung rtags kyis mgo dang mi rus la sogs na ba byung na snum bskol ba la /
T16TD4443E:361b-36: btsag yug rnams rim cha bskyed nas btab byugs pas phan zhing /
T16TD4443E:361b-41: gzer ba sogs rgyud ltar shes par bya'o //
T16TD4443E:361b-42: kye ma shar phyogs rin chen shel gyi gzhal yas na /
T16TD4443E:362a-2: sku yi rigs kyi drang srong 'khor dang bcas //
T16TD4443E:362a-3: deng 'dir zhi ba'i dbang dang byin rlabs stsol //
T16TD4443E:362a-5: kye ma lho phyogs rin chen gser gyi gzhal yas nas //
T16TD4443E:362a-6: bde chen padma ser po'i klong dkyil na //
T16TD4443E:362a-7: yon tan rigs kyi drang srong 'khor dang bcas //
T16TD4443E:362a-8: deng 'dir rgyas pa'i dbang dang byin rlabs stsol //
T16TD4443E:362a-9: nub kyi drang srong dmar po //
T16TD4443E:362a-10: kye ma nub phyogs rin chen mchong gi gzhal yas nas //
T16TD4443E:362a-11: bde chen padma dmar po'i dkyil dbus na /
T16TD4443E:362a-12: gsung gi rigs kyi drang srong 'khor dang bcas /
T16TD4443E:362a-13: deng 'dir dbang ldan dbang gi byin rlabs stsol //
T16TD4443E:362a-14: byang gi drang srong lngang [?] gu //
T16TD4443E:362a-15: kye ma byang phyogs rin chen g-yu yi gzhal yas nas //
T16TD4443E:362a-16: bde chen padma ljang gu'i gdan steng na //
T16TD4443E:362a-17: 'phrin las rigs kyi drang srong 'khor dang bcas //
T16TD4443E:362a-18: deng 'dir 'phrin las dbang dang byin rlabs stsol //
T16TD4443E:362a-19: dbus kyi drang srong mthing ga / kye ma dbus phyogs rin chen beed'ur gzhal yas nas //
T16TD4443E:362a-20: bde chen padma mthing ga'i klong dbus su //
T16TD4443E:362a-21: rigs ldan thugs kyi drang srong 'khor dang bcas //
T16TD4443E:362a-22: deng 'dir bsam tshad lhun grub dbang mchog stsol //
T16TD4443E:362a-23: khyod kyi bu brgyud slob brgyud thams cad la //
T16TD4443E:362a-24: drang srong rigs lnga sman skyong srung mar bcas //
T16TD4443E:362a-25: bskal pa ma stongs par du byin gyis rlobs //
T16TD4443E:362a-26: kye rin chen sna lnga beed'ur gzhal yas khang //
T16TD4443E:362a-27: dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ga padma'i steng /
T16TD4443E:362a-28: rigs lnga pho brang 'ja' tshon 'khrigs pa'i dbus //
T16TD4443E:362a-29: mtshan dpes rab brgyan sangs rgyas sman gyi bla //
T16TD4443E:362a-30: ye shes lnga ldan sku lnga gsal bar sprul //
T16TD4443E:362a-31: re re'i 'od la 'khor gyi drang srong dang //
T16TD4443E:362a-32: lha dang drang srong phyi nang sde bzhis bskor //
T16TD4443E:362a-33: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub rnam pa lnga'i //
T16TD4443E:362a-34: sman gyi bu mo rnam lnga gnas 'dir byon //
T16TD4443E:362a-35: dri bzang me tog glu gar du ma bcas //
T16TD4443E:362a-36: drang srong rnams la phyag dang mchod pa 'bul //
T16TD4443E:362a-48: dz'a ti zho drug / sug smel srang gang /
T16TD4443E:362a-49: pi pi ling zho drug / rgya gar gyi la la phud zho drug / kha che zho do //
T16TD4443E:362b-0: 'jam 'bras pags pa med pa zho @362b gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-2: aa ru ra rus pa med pa zho drug / shu dag zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-3: ru rta zho drug / thal dkar rdo rje zho drug / kong po'i sga zho drug / sha 'bras zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-5: zi ra nag po zho drug / pho ba ri zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-10: sle tres zho drug / byi thang ka zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-11: ba ru ra zho drug / sgog pa 'khar nyag gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-15: sa min pha la zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-17: tsi tra ka zho drug / dngul chu zho gang /
T16TD4443E:362b-18: gzi yod pa'i so ma ra tsa zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-19: bang ka dmar po'i snum nyag drug / til nag gi snum nyag gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-21: nyungs kar gyi snum nyag drug / nya cho ba dkyus mtho gang lhag tsam bcu drug gi khu ba /
T16TD4443E:362b-25: sman sprul sgor mo bubs gcig btsos pa'i khu ba ;
T16TD4443E:362b-26: phug ron gyi sha rul sums med pa bubs gcig btsos pa'i khu ba /
T16TD4443E:362b-27: 'bri mar lo bcu gnyis song ba nyag lnga /
T16TD4443E:362b-29: ra'i 'o ma phul gang sbyar ba rnams kyi byug pas /
T16TD4443E:362b-38: shu ba sogs chu ser grang ba la brten pa'i rigs mtha' dag la phan /
T16TD4443E:362b-39: nyi ma byung na dang de min me la bsros pa'i 'byug thengs gnyis byed /
T16TD4443E:362b-40: srong phyed re nad gzhi gang yod la bsku mnye zhib 'them byas pa'i lo gcig song na zhag bdun tshun la drag / na ba'i lo gnyis song na zhag bcu bzhir drag / gsum song na zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig la drag /'di khong du gtong rgyu'i sman nya phyis zho drug / la la phud zho drug / pi pi ling zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-42: kong sga zho drug / gser mdog rus med zho drug / ba ru ra zho gsum /
T16TD4443E:362b-48: so ma ra tsa zho gang /
T16TD4443E:362b-53: 'di rnams kyi khar bye dkar spar ba gang btab pa'i ril bu kham bu skam po tsam tho rangs chu skol dang yal gyis rta byas btang ngo //
T16TD4443E:363a-0: @363a * // rus gsar gyi thug pa tsha phyed tsha /
T16TD4443E:363a-1: ja la mar dang 'o ma med pa'i tsha phyed tsha ma gtogs zas kyi rigs mi gtong /
T16TD4443E:363a-2: phan yon mgo dang rna ba yan lag ma gtogs khong nad kyi rigs la phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-3: rgya gar gyi skad las mu dra phe na /
T16TD4443E:363a-4: bod skad la rgya mtsho'i s'u ba dngos /
T16TD4443E:363a-7: dz'a ti gsum cha bsnyams pa'i phye ma snum skol bar btab pa'i khu ba rna bar thigs pa gsum ri gnyis re blugs pas rna ba'i nad tsha grang kun la phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-10: rgya gar gyi dha du ra zho drug zhib par btags snum dang 'o ma gnyis skol bar btab pa lus la byugs pas chu bsags /
T16TD4443E:363a-11: pho ba spos pa na zug che ba'i rigs la phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-12: zas spyod rtsam pa dang skom li shi 'bru bdun tsam chu phor gang la spangs pa'i khu bgrang mo gtong /
T16TD4443E:363a-13: gong gi sman rnams nyin re la 'byug thengs gnyis re byed /
T16TD4443E:363a-15: sman chen ser po dang dung me la bsregs pa pho ril gsum zho la bteg pa'i ril bu pho ril tsam sgril ba khong du btang bas cham pa /
T16TD4443E:363a-17: zam ma zhu ba rnams la bsngags /
T16TD4443E:363a-18: sman ma zhu na dug ril ltag pa sprad ces pa yang 'di yin /
T16TD4443E:363a-19: 'khyags pa sogs grang ba'i nad rigs kun la phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-20: rgya gar gyi la la phud chu la thun che bar btab la skol ba'i khu ba phor pa do gsum tsam btang bas shal skyug gang rigs byung na phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-21: grang ba yun ring lo 'das 'grim pa la ko ci la me la bsregs pa dang la la phud shu dag gsum khram khrum brdungs pa thun che ba gsum zos pas phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-22: rtsam pa rtsam thug mdzo zho'i chu ras la btsags pa btang bas phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-23: pho ba 'bras bu gsum sdom chung ba la thag btang ba gcig zhib par btags pa'i khu ba mgo bo gzhogs phyed na (la nad) na gang na'i mig tu dar la btsags pa'i khu ba blugs pas phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-27: btsag rnams brdar ba'i khu ba bal mchu la byugs pas phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-28: so mar tsa brdar ba'i khu ba mig gi mtha' la byugs pas na zug che ba la phan /
T16TD4443E:363a-30: ha ha tha gha ru la gha ru ra yi ke ke ma tsu li /
T16TD4443E:363a-31: aam ge he aam gha sam ai zhes lan gsum thal ba la sngags btab na kha rlang gi dug la phan no /
